reviewText: This movie is worth the money!  Shadow Dragon Rocks the San Antonio film scene with all it's beautiful actresses that are frozen in time as captured in this  film.

This movie is alot like a home movie.  There is alot of cursing for no real reason except the lack of any real script.  It is not a movie that most people will even make it thru to the end.  Keep these few hours for something worth while.
